    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a superlative example of the 997.2 silhouette. This specimen features the 3.8L flat-six engine utilizing Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), producing a linear 385 horsepower with surgical throttle response. The mechanical state is impeccable, showing no bore scoring and maintaining factory-spec oil pressure across the entire rev range. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical locking rear differential, the chassis dynamics offer unparalleled lateral grip and composure. The braking system, headlined by four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, remains in peak operational condition with zero thermal glazing. Every bushing, linkage, and synchro operates with the tactile precision of a new vehicle. This is a concours-ready vehicle for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and documented provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
